  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is determine if the iron chelator, desferrioxamine can increase
      blood levels of hypoxia-inducible transcription factor 1 (HIF-1 protein) and to see if there
      is a corresponding increase in blood flow to the brain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
